creator: Lambus GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Lambus is the Swiss Army Knife of travelling: Everything you need for your next trip combined in one platform. Manage expenses, waypoints, travel documents, photos and more of your trip with Lambus. We assist you before, during and after your trip, so you can concentrate on the essentials: Having a great time! Plan either alone or together - the platform is able to handle both!

# Plan the next adventure together

So much world. So little time. That's why it's important to not spend unnecessary time on complicated route planning. Add, move or delete waypoints and highlights together - route planning has never been so easy. Or just let us inspire you to new goals!

# Bring order to the travel documents

No more confusing lists, tables and missing e-mails. Collect your travel documents in one place only: Lambus! This way, all fellow travelers can access it at any time - even offline!

# Expenses: Having an eye on your private and shared expenses

With Lambus you simply keep track of your expenses, even in the group. The best part: We also do the cost-splitting for you and you can even balance your costs within the app!

# Manage your private and shared notes

Regardless of whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with your group or just manage your passport number securely: Lambus is able to satisfy your needs.
descriptionShort: Manage expenses, waypoints, travel documents, photos and notes within one app!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• Starting from now, Lambus takes up to 40 % less disk space thanks to the latest technology!
• You can now sort documents and photos by their name, date and file type
• We fixed an issue where photos could not be deleted
• We fixed some minor layout issues in some areas

title: Lambus | Travel Planner

creator: Lambus GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Lambus is your new All-in-One travel app: Everything you need for your next trip combined in one platform. Manage expenses, waypoints, travel documents, photos and more of your trip with Lambus. We assist you before, during and after your trip, so you focus on having a great time during your travels! Plan either alone or together - Lambus works either way!

# Plan your next adventure

So much world. So little time. That's why it's important to not spend unnecessary time on complicated route planning. Fina new waypoints and nearby places and add them to your route - route planning has never been so easy. Or just let us inspire you to new goals!

# Import your itinerary

Planning a hiking / bicycle / motorcycle trip? Import your detailed .gpx route into Lambus easily and it will be available for everyone in your trip. Alternatively, plan a new itinerary!

# Bring order to the travel documents

No more confusing lists, tables and missing e-mails. Collect your travel documents in one place only: Lambus! This way, all fellow travelers can access it at any time - even offline!

# Expenses: Having an eye on your private and shared expenses

With Lambus you simply keep track of your expenses, even in the group. The best part: We also do the cost-splitting for you and you can even balance your costs within the app!

# Manage your private and shared notes

Regardless of whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with your group or just manage your passport number securely: Lambus is able to satisfy your needs.

# Get inspired

Be inspired by our curated trips, e.g. "West Coast USA Tour" or "Thailand May 2020" and many more!
descriptionShort: Manage expenses, waypoints, travel documents, photos and notes within one app!

We assist you before, during and after your trip, so you focus on having a great time during your travels! Plan either alone or together - Lambus works either way!

# Plan your next adventure

So much world. So little time. That's why it's important to not spend unnecessary time on complicated route planning. Fina new waypoints and nearby places and add them to your route - route planning has never been so easy. Or just let us inspire you to new goals!

# Import your itinerary

Planning a hiking / bicycle / motorcycle trip? Import your detailed .gpx route into Lambus easily and it will be available for everyone in your trip. Alternatively, plan a new itinerary!

# Bring order to the travel documents

No more confusing lists, tables and missing e-mails. Collect your travel documents in one place only: Lambus! This way, all fellow travelers can access it at any time - even offline!

# Expenses: Having an eye on your private and shared expenses

With Lambus you simply keep track of your expenses, even in the group. The best part: We also do the cost-splitting for you and you can even balance your costs within the app!

# Manage your private and shared notes

Regardless of whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with your group or just manage your passport number securely: Lambus is able to satisfy your needs.

# Get inspired

Be inspired by our curated trips, e.g. "West Coast USA Tour" or "Thailand May 2020" and many more!
descriptionShort: Manage expenses, waypoints, travel documents, photos and notes within one app!

- We improved the display of long distances
- More small improvements

We support you with various features; before, during and after your trip, so you can simply focus on enjoying it! Whether it's for a solo trip or a group trip, the Lambus trip planner is great for both!

# Plan your next adventure

So much world. So little time. All the more important not to unnecessarily waste time with planning your travel itinerary. Save your destinations as waypoints in your itinerary and add interesting places nearby. If you want to change something, simply move or delete the waypoint. Trip planning has never been this easy!

# Import your route

Planning a bike ride or motorcycle tour? Or do you want to go hiking? Just import your .gpx files from popular manufacturers like Garmin into Lambus and the itineraries are automatically available for all participants of your trip. Or plan a new route and add it to your travel itinerary.

# Bring order into your travel documents

Put an end to cluttered lists, spreadsheets and disappearing emails. Gather your travel documents in one place. That way you (and your fellow travelers) can access them at any time - even offline!

# Split expenses

Lambus makes it easy to keep track of your travel expenses. Want to split expenses on a group trip? No problem, we'll even do the math for you! Just select the expense, calculate your debts and pay them directly.

# Manage private and shared notes

Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired

Still no idea where to go on your next trip? Browse through the many travel destinations in our Discover feature and get inspired: Whether it's a road trip through the USA, a city-trip to a European metropolis or a sunny beach vacation, there's something for everybody. New exciting trips are published here weekly, fully-equipped with waypoints and travel tips!

# Book your tickets

With our Transportation feature you can not only plan your routes, but also conveniently store or book your transportation. Once booked, the tickets will automatically be added to your travel documents!
descriptionShort: Manage expenses, waypoints, travel documents, photos and notes within one app!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Thank you for using Lambus! Here is what's new:

• Get ready for the Black Friday sale in Lambus!
• Your POI notes are now shown without an additional tap
• You can now request booking offers from selected travel inspirations
• Many improvements and bug fixes to make the app even more stable

# Bring order into your travel documents

Put an end to cluttered lists, spreadsheets and disappearing emails. Gather your travel documents in one place. That way you (and your fellow travelers) can access them at any time - even offline!

# Split expenses

Lambus makes it easy to keep track of your travel expenses. Want to split expenses on a group trip? No problem, we'll even do the math for you! Just select the expense, calculate your debts and pay them directly.

# Manage private and shared notes

Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired

Still no idea where to go on your next trip? Browse through the many travel destinations in our Discover feature and get inspired: Whether it's a road trip through the USA, a city-trip to a European metropolis or a sunny beach vacation, there's something for everybody. New exciting trips are published here weekly, fully-equipped with waypoints and travel tips!

# Book your tickets

With our Transportation feature you can not only plan your routes, but also conveniently store or book your transportation. Once booked, the tickets will automatically be added to your travel documents!
descriptionShort: Manage expenses, waypoints, travel documents, photos and notes within one app!

title: Lambus | Travel Planner

creator: Lambus GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Lambus is your new All-in-One travel app: Everything you need for your next trip combined in one platform. Manage expenses, waypoints, travel documents, photos and more of your trip with Lambus. We assist you before, during and after your trip, so you focus on having a great time during your travels! Plan either alone or together - Lambus works either way!

# Plan your next adventure

So much world. So little time. That's why it's important to not spend unnecessary time on complicated route planning. Fina new waypoints and nearby places and add them to your route - route planning has never been so easy. Or just let us inspire you to new goals!

# Import your itinerary

Planning a hiking / bicycle / motorcycle trip? Import your detailed .gpx route into Lambus easily and it will be available for everyone in your trip. Alternatively, plan a new itinerary!

# Bring order to the travel documents

No more confusing lists, tables and missing e-mails. Collect your travel documents in one place only: Lambus! This way, all fellow travelers can access it at any time - even offline!

# Expenses: Having an eye on your private and shared expenses

With Lambus you simply keep track of your expenses, even in the group. The best part: We also do the cost-splitting for you and you can even balance your costs within the app!

# Manage your private and shared notes

Regardless of whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with your group or just manage your passport number securely: Lambus is able to satisfy your needs.

# Get inspired

Be inspired by our curated trips, e.g. "West Coast USA Tour" or "Thailand May 2020" and many more!
descriptionShort: Manage expenses, waypoints, travel documents, photos and notes within one app!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Thank you for using Lambus! This update contains major improvements:
• We've redesigned our trip details to bring together all the relevant information about your trip in a single view. It's now available for everyone!
• Our users asked for this one a lot: You can now attach a booking document with a specific waypoint!
• We fixed an issue where you could not override the locations during route planning (Lambus PRO only)
• More bug fixes and improvements

title: Lambus | Travel Planner

creator: Lambus GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Lambus is your new all-in-one travel app: everything you need for your next trip combined into one platform. Manage your expenses, travel documents, photos and more with Lambus. We support you with various features; before, during and after your trip, so you can simply focus on enjoying it! Whether it's for a solo trip or a group trip, the Lambus trip planner is great for both!

# Plan your next adventure

So much world. So little time. All the more important not to unnecessarily waste time with planning your travel itinerary. Save your destinations as waypoints in your itinerary and add interesting places nearby. If you want to change something, simply move or delete the waypoint. Trip planning has never been this easy!

# Import your route

Planning a bike ride or motorcycle tour? Or do you want to go hiking? Just import your .gpx files from popular manufacturers like Garmin into Lambus and the itineraries are automatically available for all participants of your trip. Or plan a new route and add it to your travel itinerary.

# Bring order into your travel documents

Put an end to cluttered lists, spreadsheets and disappearing emails. Gather your travel documents in one place. That way you (and your fellow travelers) can access them at any time - even offline!

# Split expenses

Lambus makes it easy to keep track of your travel expenses. Want to split expenses on a group trip? No problem, we'll even do the math for you! Just select the expense, calculate your debts and pay them directly.

# Manage private and shared notes

Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired

Still no idea where to go on your next trip? Browse through the many travel destinations in our Discover feature and get inspired: Whether it's a road trip through the USA, a city-trip to a European metropolis or a sunny beach vacation, there's something for everybody. New exciting trips are published here weekly, fully-equipped with waypoints and travel tips!

# Book your tickets

With our Transportation feature you can not only plan your routes, but also conveniently store or book your transportation. Once booked, the tickets will automatically be added to your travel documents!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We are thrilled to announce the new transportation view:
• You can now (finally) display a transportation through more than one waypoint
• We seamlessly merged transportation and route planning (PRO feature) into one view, so your routes are directly connected to your car/bus/train etc.
• You can now also create bicycle- and walking connections
• Distances and duration of each of your routes are now displayed directly in your itinerary

We really hope you like the changes! :-)

- Your saved accommodations are now also visible in the linked waypoint, the itinerary and the map
- Opening a notifications from the "Updates" tab now opens the dedicated screen directly, instead of always the trip details
- More bug fixes

title: Lambus | Travel Planner

creator: Lambus GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Lambus is your new all-in-one travel app: everything you need for your next trip combined into one platform. Manage your expenses, travel documents, photos and more with Lambus. We support you with various features; before, during and after your trip, so you can simply focus on enjoying it! Whether it's for a solo trip or a group trip, the Lambus trip planner is great for both!

# Plan your next adventure

So much world. So little time. All the more important not to unnecessarily waste time with planning your travel itinerary. Save your destinations as waypoints in your itinerary and add interesting places nearby. If you want to change something, simply move or delete the waypoint. Trip planning has never been this easy!

# Import your route

Planning a bike ride or motorcycle tour? Or do you want to go hiking? Just import your .gpx files from popular manufacturers like Garmin into Lambus and the itineraries are automatically available for all participants of your trip. Or plan a new route and add it to your travel itinerary.

# Bring order into your travel documents

Put an end to cluttered lists, spreadsheets and disappearing emails. Gather your travel documents in one place. That way you (and your fellow travelers) can access them at any time - even offline!

# Split expenses

Lambus makes it easy to keep track of your travel expenses. Want to split expenses on a group trip? No problem, we'll even do the math for you! Just select the expense, calculate your debts and pay them directly.

# Manage private and shared notes

Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired

Still no idea where to go on your next trip? Browse through the many travel destinations in our Discover feature and get inspired: Whether it's a road trip through the USA, a city-trip to a European metropolis or a sunny beach vacation, there's something for everybody. New exciting trips are published here weekly, fully-equipped with waypoints and travel tips!

# Book your tickets

With our Transportation feature you can not only plan your routes, but also conveniently store or book your transportation. Once booked, the tickets will automatically be added to your travel documents!
descriptionShort: Manage expenses, waypoints, travel documents, photos and notes within one app!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Thank you for using Lambus! This update contains bug fixes and improvements :-)

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Thank you for using Lambus! This update contains the following changes:
- You can now drag and drop your nearby places inside your waypoint
- You can now specify the position at which your new waypoint should be added
- You can now link or unlink waypoints in your flight, train, etc. (even after saving it)
- Lambus PRO: Open your calculated route directly in Google Maps from your itinerary
- Many more small improvements and bug fixes!

# Bring order into your travel documents

Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired

# Book your tickets

With our Transportation feature you can not only plan your routes, but also conveniently store or book your transportation. Once booked, the tickets will automatically be added to your travel documents!

# Bring order into your travel documents

Put an end to cluttered lists, spreadsheets and disappearing emails. Gather your travel documents in one place. That way you (and your fellow travelers) can access them at any time - even offline!

# Split expenses

Lambus makes it easy to keep track of your travel expenses. Want to split expenses on a group trip? No problem, we'll even do the math for you! Just select the expense, calculate your debts and pay them directly.

# Manage private and shared notes

Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired

New exciting trips are published here weekly, fully-equipped with waypoints and travel tips!

# Book your tickets

With our Transportation feature you can not only plan your routes, but also conveniently store or book your transportation. Once booked, the tickets will automatically be added to your travel documents!

Lambus is your new all-in-one travel app: everything you need for your next trip combined into one platform. Manage your expenses, travel documents, photos and more with Lambus. We support you with various features; before, during and after your trip, so you can simply focus on enjoying it! Whether it's for a solo trip or a group trip, the Lambus trip planner is great for both!

# Plan your next adventure

So much world. So little time. All the more important not to unnecessarily waste time with planning your travel itinerary. Save your destinations as stops in your itinerary and add interesting places nearby. If you want to change something, simply move or delete the stop. Trip planning has never been this easy!

# Import your route

Planning a bike ride or motorcycle tour? Or do you want to go hiking? Just import your .gpx files from popular manufacturers like Garmin into Lambus and the itineraries are automatically available for all participants of your trip. Or plan a new route and add it to your travel itinerary.

# Bring order into your travel documents

Put an end to cluttered lists, spreadsheets and disappearing emails. Gather your travel documents in one place. That way you (and your fellow travelers) can access them at any time - even offline!

# Split expenses

Lambus makes it easy to keep track of your travel expenses. Want to split expenses on a group trip? No problem, we'll even do the math for you! Just select the expense, calculate your debts and pay them directly.

# Manage private and shared notes

Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired

Still no idea where to go on your next trip? Browse through the many travel destinations in our Discover feature and get inspired: Whether it's a road trip through the USA, a city-trip to a European metropolis or a sunny beach vacation, there's something for everybody. New exciting trips are published here weekly, fully-equipped with stops and travel tips!

# Book your tickets

With our Transportation feature you can not only plan your routes, but also conveniently store or book your transportation. Once booked, the tickets will automatically be added to your travel documents!
descriptionShort: Manage expenses, itinerary, travel documents, photos and notes within one app!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Thank you for using Lambus! This update contains bug fixes and improvements :-)

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:

Planning a bike ride or motorcycle tour? Or do you want to go hiking? Just import your .gpx files from popular manufacturers like Garmin into Lambus and the itineraries are automatically available for all participants of your trip. Or plan a new route and add it to your travel itinerary.

# Bring order into your travel documents

Put an end to cluttered lists, spreadsheets and disappearing emails. Gather your travel documents in one place. That way you (and your fellow travelers) can access them at any time - even offline!

# Split expenses

Lambus makes it easy to keep track of your travel expenses. Want to split expenses on a group trip? No problem, we'll even do the math for you! Just select the expense, calculate your debts and pay them directly.

# Manage private and shared notes

Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired

Browse through the many travel destinations in our Discover feature and get inspired: Whether it's a road trip through the USA, a city-trip to a European metropolis or a sunny beach vacation, there's something for everybody. New exciting trips are published here weekly, fully-equipped with stops and travel tips!

# Book your tickets

With our Transportation feature you can not only plan your routes, but also conveniently store or book your transportation. Once booked, the tickets will automatically be added to your travel documents!

title: Lambus | Travel Planner

creator: Lambus GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Lambus is your new all-in-one travel app: everything you need for your next trip combined into one platform. Manage your expenses, travel documents, photos and more with Lambus. We support you with various features; before, during and after your trip, so you can simply focus on enjoying it! Whether it's for a solo trip or a group trip, the Lambus trip planner is great for both!

# Plan your next adventure

So much world. So little time. All the more important not to unnecessarily waste time with planning your travel itinerary. Save your destinations as stops in your itinerary and add interesting places nearby. If you want to change something, simply move or delete the stop. Trip planning has never been this easy!

# Import your route

Planning a bike ride or motorcycle tour? Or do you want to go hiking? Just import your .gpx files from popular manufacturers like Garmin into Lambus and the itineraries are automatically available for all participants of your trip. Or plan a new route and add it to your travel itinerary.

# Bring order into your travel documents

Put an end to cluttered lists, spreadsheets and disappearing emails. Gather your travel documents in one place. That way you (and your fellow travelers) can access them at any time - even offline!

# Split expenses

Lambus makes it easy to keep track of your travel expenses. Want to split expenses on a group trip? No problem, we'll even do the math for you! Just select the expense, calculate your debts and pay them directly.

# Manage private and shared notes

Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired

Still no idea where to go on your next trip? Browse through the many travel destinations in our Discover feature and get inspired: Whether it's a road trip through the USA, a city-trip to a European metropolis or a sunny beach vacation, there's something for everybody. New exciting trips are published here weekly, fully-equipped with stops and travel tips!

# Book your tickets

With our Transportation feature you can not only plan your routes, but also conveniently store or book your transportation. Once booked, the tickets will automatically be added to your travel documents!

title: Lambus | Travel Planner

creator: Lambus GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Lambus - Your all-in-one travel companion!

Conquer the world with ease and plan your next adventure with Lambus - the ultimate travel app that has everything you need for your trip! From trip planning to organizing your documents to managing expenses, we've got it all under control so you can focus on your adventure! Whether you're traveling solo or on a group adventure, Lambus is your reliable companion on every trip.

# Simply plan, experience more!
So much world, so little time! That's why we've made itinerary planning as easy as possible. Mark your destinations as stops and add interesting places effortlessly. Want to change something? No problem! Move or delete your stops in a snap. Planning your trip has never been so easy!

# Import itineraries made easy
Whether you're planning a bike tour, motorcycle tour or hiking adventure - with Lambus you can easily import .gpx files from popular manufacturers like Garmin and all participants of your trip will have instant access to the itineraries. Or you can simply create a new route directly in our route planner.

# Everything in one place - No more chaos in your documents
No more confusing lists and lost emails! With Lambus, you collect all your travel documents in one safe place. So you (and your travel companions) can access them at any time, even offline!

# Keep travel expenses under control
Lambus makes it easy to keep track of your travel expenses. You're on a group trip and want to split the expenses? No problem! We'll even do the math for you! Just fill in the form, calculate your debts and pay directly.

# Manage practical notes
Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired!
Still no idea where to go next? Browse through our Discover feature and get inspired by the many destinations. Whether it's an exciting road trip through the USA, a city break in a European metropolis or a relaxing beach vacation - you'll find it here. Every day we publish exciting trips with stops and travel tips!

# Book your tickets
With our transportation feature, you can not only plan routes between stops, but also easily deposit or book your transportation. Once you book your tickets, they are automatically added to your travel documents!

Visiting more than one place? Lambus is the ultimate travel app for backpackers, road trippers and world travelers! Plan your next adventure effortlessly with our innovative travel planner. What are you waiting for? Download Lambus and start your next adventure with us! 🌍🎒✈️
descriptionShort: Manage expenses, itinerary, travel documents, photos and notes within one app!

# Import itineraries made easy
Whether you're planning a bike tour, motorcycle tour or hiking adventure - with Lambus you can easily import .gpx files from popular manufacturers like Garmin and all participants of your trip will have instant access to the itineraries. Or you can simply create a new route directly in our route planner.

# Everything in one place - No more chaos in your documents
No more confusing lists and lost emails! With Lambus, you collect all your travel documents in one safe place. So you (and your travel companions) can access them at any time, even offline!

# Keep travel expenses under control
Lambus makes it easy to keep track of your travel expenses. You're on a group trip and want to split the expenses? No problem! We'll even do the math for you! Just fill in the form, calculate your debts and pay directly.

# Manage practical notes
Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired!
Still no idea where to go next? Browse through our Discover feature and get inspired by the many destinations. Whether it's an exciting road trip through the USA, a city break in a European metropolis or a relaxing beach vacation - you'll find it here. Every day we publish exciting trips with stops and travel tips!

# Book your tickets
With our transportation feature, you can not only plan routes between stops, but also easily deposit or book your transportation. Once you book your tickets, they are automatically added to your travel documents!

Visiting more than one place? Lambus is the ultimate travel app for backpackers, road trippers and world travelers! Plan your next adventure effortlessly with our innovative travel planner. What are you waiting for? Download Lambus and start your next adventure with us! 🌍🎒✈️
